ZH: 我昨天乘坐公交车去了饭店。
EN: Yesterday, I took the bus to the restaurant.

ZH: 他每天都乘坐地铁上班。
EN: He commutes to work by subway every day.

ZH: 我们乘坐出租车去了机场。
EN: We took a taxi to the airport.

ZH: 她乘坐飞机去了上海。
EN: She flew to Shanghai.

ZH: 他们乘坐邮轮去欧洲旅行了一个月。
EN: They traveled to Europe for a month by cruise ship.

ZH: 孩子们很开心地乘坐旋转木马。
EN: The children happily rode the carousel.

ZH: 我们乘坐摩天轮欣赏城市的风景。
EN: We rode the Ferris wheel to enjoy the city view.

ZH: 她害怕乘坐过山车。
EN: She is afraid of riding roller coasters.

ZH: 我们乘坐有空调的大巴去了山区。
EN: We took an air-conditioned bus to the mountains.

ZH: 我们乘坐小船划到岛上。
EN: We rowed a small boat to the island.

ZH: 他们乘坐电梯上了楼。
EN: They took the elevator to go upstairs.

ZH: 我们乘坐有轨电车穿过城市的繁华区。
EN: We rode the tram through the bustling area of the city.

ZH: 她乘坐自行车回家。
EN: She rode her bike home.

ZH: 我们乘坐缆车上山看日出。
EN: We took the cable car up the mountain to watch the sunrise.

ZH: 他们乘坐火车去了西部。
EN: They took the train to the west.

ZH: 我们乘坐热气球飞过了城市。
EN: We flew over the city in a hot air balloon.

ZH: 孩子们很期待乘坐游乐园的过山车。
EN: The children are looking forward to riding the roller coaster at the amusement park.

ZH: 我们乘坐渡轮穿过了湖泊。
EN: We took a ferry across the lake.

ZH: 她乘坐直升机飞越了雪山。
EN: She flew over the snowy mountains in a helicopter.

ZH: 我们乘坐单车环游了整个城市。
EN: We rode bikes around the entire city.
